Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:22.40,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I scowled at the wind blowing\Nat my window of boredom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:30.43,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so I could turn away\Nthe awkwardness I was feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:38.61,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:44.13,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I nod noncommittally at today\Nas I hold it in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:49.51,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,projecting myself a little exaggeratedly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:54.89,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that\Nsomething is about to change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:03:00.22,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you\Ncalling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:06.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking up at cloudy skies,\NI sense what's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:14.85,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's reach out our hands\Nwith courage stronger than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:19.79,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and shadow are both still far off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:26.13,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but even so, we want to know\Nthe reason for this kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:33.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go look now, beyond the brilliance\Nthat goes by nobody's name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:41.63,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,before it all becomes a thing of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:51.73,SignsT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(157,269)}The Truth About the Historic\NClassic Lit Club
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:06.03,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Classic Lit Club President\NSekitani Jun
