Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:07.70,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sure that ten years from now,\NI won't regret spending this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:54.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"It was in no way a heroic tale"
