Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:16:00.46,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Rally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:09.36,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"On strike! Right is on our side!\NTeachers accept our demands!"
