Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.61,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Sekitani ('Kanya')
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.12,0:27:08.05,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.08,0:27:11.81,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.84,0:27:15.81,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.84,0:27:21.18,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Our snooze-time date
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.40,0:27:41.40,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat of your budding warmth troubles me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:52.16,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand how I feel yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.54,0:27:59.02,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't supposed to be\Nany significance in your glance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.05,0:28:04.44,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's the same one\Nyou give all your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.47,0:28:10.11,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The tiny wishing star fading\Ninto the morning light
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:15.16,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and the magic it works during the night\N(I wish you would notice)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:18.12,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it turns to love
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.15,0:28:21.88,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me in a pleasant dream
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:25.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure that you find me, okay?
